review_blob: This is the worst tasting beer, if I can include taste at all, I have ever had.  It is so watered down and disgusting.
Very nice orangy taste going down.  After taste  is a complete compliment to the smell and first taste.
Trying not to be biased against ale, this beer still didnt cut it.  Redhook seemed a bit flat for my taste.
for such a nice bottle, I expected this beer to be much better than what it was.
